OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry start with sunny spells,
OL,6,Fbut cloud soon thickening, with a band
OL,7,Fof rain spreading southeast. This
OL,8,Fclearing by mid-afternoon to colder,
OL,9,Fbreezier and brighter conditions, with
OL,10,Foccasional blustery showers.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy with occasional
OL,13,Fshowers at first becoming more settled
OL,14,Fovernight and partly cloudy at times,
OL,15,Fwhich with easing winds could lead to
OL,16,Fsome frost patches forming by the
OL,17,Fmorning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
