OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FCold start Friday, with some
OL,6,Ffrost, then sunny intervals. Stronger
OL,7,Fwinds overnight with patchy rain,
OL,8,Fbecoming more widespread by the
OL,9,Fmorning.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,12,FSunshine and blustery showers, feeling
OL,13,Frather cool at times, during Saturday
OL,14,Fand Sunday. Monday will see winds
OL,15,Feasing but remains showery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
